lead_paragraph: Duke's Grayson Allen sat at his locker, his head hanging and voice barely registering much louder than a whisper. He couldn't explain to a crowd of reporters huddled around him why he had tripped an opponent during a game for the third time in a year.

headline.print_headline: No. 5 Duke Beats Elon 72-61 in Final Game Before ACC Play
